     C*
     C           NGOKE     DIV  #SYOS     WWHAK2  71
     C           WWHAK2    ADD  0.9       WKHAK2
     C*
     C                     ADD  WKHAK1    QKHAK1
     C                     ADD  WKHAK2    QKHAK2
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
